A18. Discover two hallucination cases when using a generative AI system.
A cupple of months ago I asking AIs questions about university for my brother, and some of it answer are wrong.

  First, when I ask about scolarship for Newcastle university. I ask if the scorlarship give 7000 for each year or 7000 for the whole degree.
The AI said it is 7000 for the whole degree, but if you check in their website it clearly state that it is for every year.

  Second, when I ask it to list university in a Russell group, it also list University of Aberdeen and University of Leicester. 
This is wrong because if you look in the website both are not list as part of the group.
